parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS can cause the brakes to lock up, leading to extended stopping distances, loss of control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brakes lock up too easily
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the ABS activates unnecessarily
the brake pedal is difficult to press
the wheels lock up
and the vehicle is hard to control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unnecessary activation of the ABS can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, loss of control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ABS activates without cause
the brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop
and the wheels lock up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to extended stopping distances, loss of control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the brakes are difficult to press
and the vehicle takes longer to stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS warning light can cause the driver to be unaware of potential brake system problems, leading to increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ABS warning light remains on even when there is no issue.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt retractor can lead to inadequate restraint in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or fatality. Additionally, a malfunctioning seatbelt may prevent occupants from using it properly, further compromising safety.
symptoms: The seatbelt does not retract
the seatbelt does not extend
the seatbelt does not provide an audible click when latched
occupants are unsure if the seatbelt is properly buckled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the windshield wipers can reduce the driver's visibility, increasing the risk of a vehicle crash, especially during rainy or snowy conditions.
symptoms: Windshield wipers work intermittently
windshield wipers stop working suddenly
windshield wipers do not turn on
windshield wipers turn on and off randomly.
